column5: Went down to a local creek caught some suckers catfish 3 rainbows and 4 of these im not sure if they're white perch or white bass.My buddy got his first sucker.
That second fish looks like a rock bass. Great pics tho, nice trout!
cool pics.  Rock bass for sure.
ya that picture made it look  green but it was more silver
catch and release? not bad nice colors

nice rainbows there!  2nd picture looks like a rock bass to me....  Any silver bass / perch I've had have been completely white... not black spots at all on them, except maybe a really thin black lateral line.
There's no question that is a rock bass.
Great report and pics johnl  Thanks for sharing Leechman
Rock bass for sure..... very tasty..... rainbows nice to... but its no rock bass.....  http://www.ofncommunity.com/forums/index.p...0bass&st=20
nice selection of fish you had...great pics too....thats a rock bass 100%
Very nice colors on that bow!
